overview: She's still saving the world. Only now we see her at home, as well as on top of 30-story buildings, socking villians.  Speaking of villians, evil Leena's in this one too, along with beautiful exotic Asia Carrera, hot rocket blonde Kaitlyn Ashley, and stacked DDD'er Rebecca Wilde!  They may not be Superman or Spiderman. But man, they are horny!  Supermodel 2. To the rescue!
tagline: Pare hero. Part Model. All Woman.
title: Supermodel 2
